data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3/2.5 end unit townhome in the Green Valley Villages! Conveniently located between I-75 and the McDonough Square, this home has much to offer including a spacious back yard, stainless steel appliances, plus a 1 car garage! Master has a garden tub, separate shower, and spacious walk in closet. Relax on warm sunny days in the community swimming pool.
